squad.Discovery.implications | hasValue | Either subtext has a per-peer delivery edge case, or peers can mute/block specific senders and the sender gets no signal of it. Either way, send_message reporting 'Message sent' is not the same as 'Message received' — the sender lacks a reliable read receipt.
